'''We Came as Romans'''是一個[[美國|美國]][[金屬蕊|金屬蕊]]樂團，來自[[密西根州|密西根州]]的特洛伊，不過大家所熟知的是他們以[[底特律|底特律]]為家鄉。成軍於2005年，在2009年四月與[[Equal_Vision唱片|Equal Vision唱片]]簽約，並發行兩張EP《Demonstrations》和《Dreams》，兩者都在2009年，經過一、兩年的創作，又在2009年與2011年分別發行專輯《To Plant a Seed》與《Understanding What We've Grown to Be》。樂團更在美國、加拿大、歐洲、紐西蘭及澳洲巡演。

==樂團歷史==
===發跡===
2005年八月，還是中學生的Sean N. Zelda、David Stephens、Jonny Nabors、Mark Myatt和Joshua Moore萌生組團的念頭－「This Emergency」就這樣誕生了，當時David Stephens的職位是吉他，在底特律一帶作表演。2005年十一月，
他是We Came as Romans的前身，隨著成員的交替，樂團改名成We Came as Romans。貝斯手Sean E. Daly取代Jonny Nabors的位置。隔年六月，Sean N. Zelda加入密西根大學，進而離開樂團。2006年的夏天，樂團的友人Larry Clark正式加入樂團，成為新主唱，樂團正式更名為We Came as Romans。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.last.fm/music/This+Emergency |title=This Emergency – Discover music, concerts, stats, & pictures at |publisher=Last.fm |date=2008-11-21 |accessdate=2010-07-02 |archive-date=2016-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201175538/http://www.last.fm/music/This+Emergency }}</ref>根據令一位主唱David Stephens的說法，當時錄製了兩首新歌分別是"[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=repFZnnIFrs Mouth to Mouth] {{Wayback|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=repFZnnIFrs |date=20160929185710 }}"與原版的Colours，與新主唱共同錄製的。

===第一張Demo作品與EP《To Plant a Seed》===
經過換名與一些成員的更替，樂團首先發行一張DEMO（有些人稱之為EP《Motions》）在演唱會與線上銷售一空，隨後在十二月發行了《Dream》這張EP，音樂製作人Joey Sturgis，在第一個禮拜就超過50000份數位下載，這張作品獲得音樂界的好評，<ref>[http://www.absolutepunk.net/showthread.php?t=1099972 WCAR review at ABSOLUTEPUNK]</ref>音樂評論[[AbsolutePunk|AbsolutePunk]]給了79/100分，而Sputnikmusic給了3.5/分，他們說這張EP「簡短而甜美，但不朽又懷抱夢想」。<ref>[http://www.sputnikmusic.com/album.php?albumid=33932 WCAR review at SPUTNIK]</ref>在這兩張EP的發行其間，樂團參與《V-Neck & Shaved Chest巡迴》，與樂團[[Close_to_Home|Close to Home]]。

接著他們聲援樂團[[Oh,_Sleeper|Oh, Sleeper]]和[[The_Chariot|The Chariot]]的共同主場巡演《Here a tour, there a tour, everywhere a tour tour》，從2009年九月到十一月。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metalunderground.com/news/details.cfm?newsid=48235 |title=Oh, Sleeper - News Article |publisher=www.metalunderground.com |date= |accessdate=2011-01-10 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170435/http://www.metalunderground.com/news/details.cfm?newsid=48235 }}</ref>

===巡迴和第一張專輯《To Plant a Seed》===
後來，唱片公司''Equal Vision''與簽約，隔年十一月3日透過該公司發行《To Plant a Seed》，重新錄製歌曲《Dreams》和《Intentions》，其中歌手Tyler "Telle" Smith也在其中演唱。年底之時他們同[[I_See_Stars|I See Stars]]、[[Of_Mice_&_Men|Of Mice & Men]]和[[Broadway|Broadway]]完成《Leave It to the Suits巡迴》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiestar.tv/grafwall/2009/09/leave-it-to-suits-tour-w-i-see-stars.html|title=Leave It To The Suits - News Article|publisher=www.indiestar.tv|date=|accessdate=2011-01-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111007224337/http://www.indiestar.tv/grafwall/2009/09/leave-it-to-suits-tour-w-i-see-stars.html|archivedate=2011-10-07}}</ref>

2010年，We Came as Romans與許許多多的團體進行巡迴。首先是一月參加樂團[[Alesana|Alesana]]的《The Emptiness巡迴》，另外還有[[A_Skylit_Drive|A Skylit Drive]]、[[The_Word_Alive|The Word Alive]]和[[Of_Mice_&_Men|Of Mice & Men]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.myspace.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=blog.view&friendId=69317&blogId=522300340 |title=The Emptiness Tour - MySpace-blog | van Fearless Records |publisher=Blogs.myspace.com |date= |accessdate=2010-07-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207065936/http://blogs.myspace.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=blog.view |archivedate=2009-02-07 }}</ref>主場表演《We Are Not Meaningless巡迴》，與樂團[[Four_Letter_Lie|Four Letter Lie]]和Life on Repeat。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theprp.com/2010/04/05/news/we-came-as-romans-reveal-aprilmay-dates-with-four-letter-lie/ |title=WCAR The PRP |publisher=ThePRP.com |date= |accessdate=2011-08-08 |archive-date=2021-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507042805/https://www.theprp.com/2010/04/05/news/we-came-as-romans-reveal-aprilmay-dates-with-four-letter-lie/ }}</ref>另外在五、六月與[[Asking_Alexandria|Asking Alexandria]]、[[From_First_to_Last|From First to Last]]、[[Our_Last_Night|Our Last Night]]和[[A_Bullet_for_Pretty_Boy|A Bullet for Pretty Boy]]參加《The Welcome to the Circus巡迴》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.absolutepunk.net/showthread.php?t=1580591 |title=Welcome to the Circus Tour - News Article |publisher=AbsolutePunk.net |date= |accessdate=2010-07-02}}</ref>，以宣傳新專輯。首支音樂單曲影帶《To Plant a Seed》在五月11日發行於[[iTunes|iTunes]]。六月11日，透過樂團的[[Facebook|Facebook]]與[[Twitter|Twitter]]頁面，宣布將與製作人Joey Sturgis進入錄音室的消息。錄製的時間從六月15日到六月20日。<ref name="Joey Sturgis' Recording Schedule">{{Cite web |url=http://calendar.yahoo.com/joeyismusic/public/month?date=20100611 |title=Joey Sturgis' Recording Schedule |access-date=2011-11-05 |archive-date=2011-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928061022/http://calendar.yahoo.com/joeyismusic/public/month?date=20100611 }}</ref>單曲《To Move on Is to Grow》就這樣發布了。下半年，We Came as Romans又參加了《Scream It Like You Mean It 2010巡迴》，這次表演的陣容有：[[Silverstein|Silverstein]]、[[Emery|Emery]]、[[Dance_Gavin_Dance|Dance Gavin Dance]]、[[I_Set_My_Friends_On_Fire|I Set My Friends On Fire]]、[[Sky_Eats_Airplane|Sky Eats Airplane]]、[[Ivoryline|Ivoryline]]與Close to Home<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.screamitlikeyoumeanit.com/ |title=Scream It Like You Mean It - Website |publisher=ScreamItLikeYouMeanIt.com |date= |accessdate=2011-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100520041551/http://www.screamitlikeyoumeanit.com/ |archive-date=2010-05-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>八月到十月，在美家地區與[[In_Fear_and_Faith|In Fear and Faith]]、[[Confide|Confide]]、Upon a Burning Body以及[[Abandon_All_Ships|Abandon All Ships]]參與《Band of Brothers巡迴》。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://punkmusic.about.com/b/2010/08/24/we-came-as-romans-announce-band-of-brothers-tour.htm |title=Punk Music - News Article |publisher=PunkMusic.com |date= |accessdate=2011-01-07 |archive-date=2015-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150412065418/http://punkmusic.about.com/b/2010/08/24/we-came-as-romans-announce-band-of-brothers-tour.htm }}</ref>十月與十一月，他們轉換到歐洲參加《Never Say Die巡演》，和樂團[[Parkway_Drive|Parkway Drive]]、[[Comeback_Kid|Comeback Kid]]、[[Bleeding_Through|Bleeding Through]]、[[War_from_a_Harlots_Mouth|War from a Harlots Mouth]]、[[Emmure|Emmure]]、[[Your_Demise|Your Demise]]共同演出。<ref name="altpress.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/we_came_as_romans_release_new_song_announce_australian_tour/# |title=AltPress.com - News Article |publisher=AltPress.com |date= |accessdate=2011-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101123210802/http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/we_came_as_romans_release_new_song_announce_australian_tour/ |archive-date=2010-11-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>最後在年底《No Sleep Til音樂祭》到澳洲一帶與樂團[[麥加帝斯|麥加帝斯]]（[[:en:Magadeth|Megadeth]]）巡演。<ref name="altpress.com"/>同時，十一月由[[Fearless唱片|Fearless唱片]]發行的合輯《Punk Goes Pop 3》收錄了他們翻唱[[賈斯汀·提姆布萊克|賈斯汀·提姆布萊克]]的歌曲《My Love》。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ampmagazine.com/6073/punk-goes-amp/ |title=AmpMagazine.com - News Article |publisher=AmpMagazine.com |date= |accessdate=2011-01-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110115135221/http://www.ampmagazine.com/6073/punk-goes-amp/ |archivedate=2011-01-15 }}</ref>他們在官方頁面表示，他們將在明年第一表演中，初次演唱這首歌曲，但也是最後一次。十一月14日，第二支音樂影帶《To Move on Is to Grow》在[[iTunes|iTunes]]上釋出，新專輯主打歌《To Plant a Seed》出現在十二月21日的合輯《Equal Vision唱片鉅獻：2011新聲代》（Equal Vision Records Presents: New Sounds 2011）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.equalvision.com/news/show/606 |title=Equal Vision Records Presents: New Sounds 2011 |publisher=Equal Vision Records |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921055114/http://www.equalvision.com/news/show/606 |archivedate=2013-09-21 |accessdate=2011-11-05 }}</ref>2011年一月6日，唱片公司宣布出道專輯《To Plant a Seed》將與新單曲《To Move on Is to Grow》組合成CD/DVD豪華盤發行，將獨家在18日於下列通路販售：Merchnow.com、iTunes與F.Y.E。其中DVD有38分的獨家專訪、幕後花絮、當時在美國的現場演出與新MV《To Move on Is to Grow》。

儘管作品《[[To_Plant_a_Seed|To Plant a Seed]]》重發的第一次錄音一直到2011年的二、三月才被確定，<ref name="Joey Sturgis' Recording Schedule"/> We Came as Romans已經參與一月份在[[科羅拉多州|科羅拉多州]][[丹佛|丹佛]]的《Motel 6 Rock Yourself to Sleep巡迴》，與樂團[[Woe,_Is_Me|Woe, Is Me]]、[[For_Today|For Today]]、[[The_Word_Alive|The Word Alive]]和同公司的樂團[[Texas_in_July|Texas in July]]，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rockyourselftosleep.com/ |title=RockYourselfToSleep.com |publisher=RockYourselfToSleep.com |date= |accessdate=2011-01-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715195114/http://rockyourselftosleep.com/ |archivedate=2011-07-15 }}</ref>，更與[[Silverstein|Silverstein]]在一同參加了''Outerloop Presents''所舉辦的音樂活動《Amped and Alive》，該年的活動主題為 ''Ice Jam''。一月10日，《Rock Yourself to Sleep巡迴》不過五天，唱片公司[[Equal_Vision唱片|Equal Vision]]發出了緊急聲明，關於吉他手Joshua Moore的身體狀況：「在今早，We Came as Romans的吉他手Joshua Moore被診斷出細菌性感染的腦膜炎，目前在[[內布拉斯加州|內布拉斯加州]]的一所醫院中。」根據貝斯手Andy Glass：「看到Joshua的情況實在是太突然了，但我們希望大家可以祈禱，使他早日康復，也謝謝所有歌迷明白我們現在困難的處境。」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://blog.equalvision.com/post/2689149147/we-came-as-romans-official-announcement|title=WE CAME AS ROMANS - OFFICIAL ANNOUNCEMENT|date=2011-01-10|accessdate=2011-11-05|archive-date=2015-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120110701/http://blog.equalvision.com/post/2689149147/we-came-as-romans-official-announcement}}</ref>故此接下來的巡迴他將不會參與，然而二月1日，透過Moore的[[Twitter|Twitter]]和[[Facebook|Facebook]]，在醫生第二次的診斷下，他可能可以重新參與巡演。二月3日，他在[[賓州|賓州]]的[[蘭開斯特_(賓夕法尼亞州)|蘭開斯特]]與樂團會合。在Joshua Moore的病康復初期，樂團由於天氣因素取消在[[丹佛|丹佛]]和[[鹽湖城|鹽湖城]]的表演。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.equalvision.com/news/show/611|title=EqualVision.com|publisher=EqualVision.com|date=|accessdate=2011-01-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110114210759/http://equalvision.com/news/show/611|archivedate=2011-01-14}}</ref>

三月他們為樂團[[A_Day_to_Remember|A Day to Remember]]的《Game Changers巡迴》發聲，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.equalvision.com/news/show/602/ |title=EqualVision.com |publisher=EqualVision.com |date= |accessdate=2011-01-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101224020836/http://www.equalvision.com/news/show/602 |archivedate=2010-12-24 }}</ref>並在四月成為《Scream It Like You Mean It 2011歐洲巡迴》的主場，表演的樂團還有[[Miss_May_I|Miss May I]]、[[The_Word_Alive|The Word Alive]]與[[This_or_the_Apocalypse|This or the Apocalypse]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.screamitlikeyoumeanit.com/|title=ScreamItLikeYouMeanIt.com|publisher=www.screamitlikeyoumeanit.com|date=|accessdate=2011-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100520041551/http://www.screamitlikeyoumeanit.com/|archive-date=2010-05-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>《To Plant a Seed》第二部分的錄音在五月到六月展開。<ref name="Joey Sturgis' Recording Schedule"/>十二月8日，他們被宣布為2011年六月到八月的《Warped巡演》的第一批樂團，將在整個巡迴中表演。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://punkmusic.about.com/od/Warpedtour2011/a/The-2011-Vans-Warped-Tour-Lineup.htm |title=PunkMusic.about.com |publisher=PunkMusic.about.com |date= |accessdate=2011-01-10 |archive-date=2016-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520143732/http://punkmusic.about.com/od/Warpedtour2011/a/The-2011-Vans-Warped-Tour-Lineup.htm }}</ref>

===專輯《Understanding What We've Grown To Be》===

根據唱片公司表示：「目前樂團正在創作他們的第二張正規專輯，將會在巡迴中與製作人Joey Sturgis錄音，預計在2011年的秋天發行。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.equalvision.com/artist/We_Came_As_Romans|title=EqualVision.com|publisher=EqualVision.com|date=|accessdate=2011-06-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110903185535/http://www.equalvision.com/artist/We_Came_As_Romans|archivedate=2011-09-03}}</ref>在與提神飲料''Monster Energy''的專屬記者（Monster Energy Pit reporter）的Brian Walsh的訪談中，Joshua Moore證實第二張專輯的計畫已經完成了，他們在《[[Warped巡迴|Warped巡迴]]》前就會進入錄音室了。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ArQ6cEX8OMA|title=YouTube.com|publisher=YouTube.com|date=|accessdate=2011-06-18|archive-date=2016-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160129142426/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ArQ6cEX8OMA}}</ref>

在那時候，We Came as Romans出現在雜誌''Substream Music Press''六月號與七月號的中，Dave Stephens則是出現在雜誌''Alternative Press''八月號。同時被《[[Warped巡迴|Warped巡迴]]》官方給高亮起來。

2011年九月13日終於推出專輯《Understanding What We’ve Grown To Be》。在發行前夕在[[Equal_Vision唱片|Equal Vision唱片]]的[[Youtube|Youtube]]頁面發布首支單曲《Mis//Understanding》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.altpress.com/features/entry/in_the_studio_exclusive_news_we_came_as_romans/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-11-06 |archive-date=2017-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701204906/http://www.altpress.com/features/entry/in_the_studio_exclusive_news_we_came_as_romans/ }}</ref>與專輯的同名歌曲《Understanding What We've Grown to Be》也隨後發布。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mmtyIOGafVY&feature=related |title=We Came As Romans YouTube |publisher=Equal Vision Records |date= |accessdate=2011-08-24 |archive-date=2016-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161213204905/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mmtyIOGafVY&feature=related }}</ref>這兩首歌曲提前在七月5日時於[[iTunes|iTunes]]上預購。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://itunes.apple.com/us/preorder/mis-understanding-single/id445420994 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-11-06 |archive-date=2018-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825215621/https://itunes.apple.com/us/preorder/mis-understanding-single/id445420994 }}</ref>除了歌曲以外，專輯封面透過樂團的官網也於14日上傳至網路。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wecameasromans.com/reveal/|title=WeCameAsRomans.com|publisher=http://www.takeoverstudio.com/%20target=|date=|accessdate=2011-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718102715/http://wecameasromans.com/reveal/|archive-date=2011-07-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

根據樂團指出：「不論是在音樂上或是在歌詞上，《Understanding What We've Grown to Be》比先前的作品《To Plant a Seed》都還要黑暗一點。但仍然保有樂團整體正面與兄弟情誼的風格，新的題材更直接的接近生活中的奮鬥與成長中的挑戰。」<ref name="wecameasromans.com">{{cite web|url=http://wecameasromans.com/|title=WeCameAsRomans.com|publisher=http://www.takeoverstudio.com/%20target=|date=|accessdate=2011-07-15|archive-date=2015-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717084412/http://wecameasromans.com/}}</ref>接著八月24日他們發出了這張專輯最後一張單曲《What I Wished I Never Had》，於Youtube。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cDWEs2W15fU&feature=player_embedded |title=We Came As Romans YouTube |publisher=Equal Vision Records |date= |accessdate=2011-08-24 |archive-date=2016-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161213204908/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cDWEs2W15fU&feature=player_embedded }}</ref>專輯發行當天，音樂零售商[[Hot_Topic|Hot Topic]]發行《AP雜誌We Came As Romans限量版迷你雜誌》（Alternative Press Limited Edition We Came As Romans Mini Magazine），裡頭附贈了「I'm Alive」手環與主打單曲《Understanding What We've Grown To Be》CD。<ref name="www.HotTopic.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.hottopic.com/hottopic/WhatsNew/Music/AP-Alternative-Press-Limited-Edition-We-Came-As-Romans-Mini-Magazine-PreOrder-307685.jsp |title=We Came As Romans Hot Topic Release |publisher=HotTopic.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-14 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924031412/http://www.hottopic.com/hottopic/WhatsNew/Music/AP-Alternative-Press-Limited-Edition-We-Came-As-Romans-Mini-Magazine-PreOrder-307685.jsp }}</ref>該專輯獲得[[告示牌|告示牌200]]第20位、獨立榜第7位、硬派專輯榜第5位、現代搖滾榜第10位，一直到九月底，他們在''告示牌200''上仍在第103位中。在歐洲方面，專輯《Understanding What We've Grown to Be》由重金屬唱片公司[[Nuclear_Blast|Nuclear Blast]]代理發行。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.musicreview.co.za/2011/07/21/we-came-as-romans-sign-european-deal-with-nuclear-blast/|publisher=Music Review|title=Deadlink|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140427221230/http://www.musicreview.co.za/2011/07/21/we-came-as-romans-sign-european-deal-with-nuclear-blast/|archivedate=2014-04-27|accessdate=2011-11-06}}</ref>

在樂團[[Miss_May_I|Miss May I]]、[[Of_Mice_&_Men|Of Mice & Men]]、[[Texas_in_July|Texas in July]]和[[Close_to_Home|Close to Home]]的聲援下，We Came As Romans在九月份展開《I'm Alive巡迴》。<ref name="wecameasromans.com"/>同時，十月中旬，他們和[[Close_to_Home|Close to Home]]參與位於[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[肯特_(俄亥俄州)|肯特]]的音樂祭《The Outpost》，樂團Worth The Wait、Ionia也在該天演出。另外，在樂團[[The_Devil_Wears_Prada|The Devil Wears Prada]]展開《Dead Throne巡迴》之時，We Came as Romans也飛到澳洲為他們支援，其中同台演出的樂團有[[Dream_On,_Dreamer|Dream On, Dreamer]]。接著，由''Whooznxt.com''和''Headbang for the Highway''所舉辦的《World War III巡演》，他們也沒有缺席，巡演主場為[[Hollywood_Undead|Hollywood Undead]]與[[Asking_Alexandria|Asking Alexandria]]，參與的藝人還有[[Borgore|Borgore]]、[[Destroy_Rebuild_Until_God_Shows|Destroy Rebuild Until God Shows]]。在[[加州|加州]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]由''Soundcheck Hollywood''所舉辦的活動《A Reckless Halloween》，找來了[[槍與玫瑰|槍與玫瑰]]的前鼓手Steven Adler，還有樂團[[Destroy_Rebuild_Until_God_Shows|Destroy Rebuild Until God Shows]]、[[Winds_of_Plague|Winds of Plague]]、[[Stick_to_Your_Guns|Stick To Your Guns]]與本樂團。We Came as Romans也預計將成為''Merchnow.com''與''EveryConcertEver.com''所舉辦的《Take A Picture, It Will Last Longer巡迴》的主場秀，同場加演的樂團有[[Falling_In_Reverse|Falling In Reverse]]、[[Sleeping_with_Sirens|Sleeping with Sirens]]、[[Atilla|Atilla]]與[[For_All_I_Am|For All I Am]]。<ref name="equalvision.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.equalvision.com/news/show/688|title=equalvision.com|publisher=equalvision.com|date=|accessdate=2011-09-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221100952/http://www.equalvision.com/news/show/688|archivedate=2014-02-21}}</ref>2012年，將與[[Alesana|Alesana]]成為《Macbeth Footwear and Keep A Breast歐洲巡演》的主場，支援的樂團則是有[[Iwrestledabearonce|Iwrestledabearonce]]、[[Glamour_of_the_Kill|Glamour of the Kill]]，並在二月到日本的《Scream Out音樂祭》作演出。

